        "content": "<div class=\"netsage-banner\">\n  <table class=\"netsage-nav\" style=\"width: 100%; border: none;\">\n    <tr>\n      <th><h2>File Transfer Data:</h2></th>\n    <tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/xk26IFhmk?from=${__from}&to=${__to}\">What are the top sources/destinations of file transfers?</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/QfzDJKhik?from=${__from}&to=${__to}\">What are the top transfers by organization?</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/-l3_u8nWk?from=${__from}&to=${__to}\">What do individual transfers between sites look like?</a></li>\n          <li><a class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/CJC1FFhmz?from=${__from}&to=${__to}\">What are the current file transfer data summary statistics?</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </td>\n      \n  </table>\n  <div class=\"netsage-column\">\n\n    \n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .netsage-banner {\n  background-color: #618ED0;\n  padding: 1rem 15rem;\n  }\n  a.netsage-button-q {\n  color: white;\n  background-color: #759FDD;\n  padding: 4px;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  }\n  a.netsage-button-q:hover {\n  color: white;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav tr, .netsage-nav td, .netsage-nav th{\n  border: none !important;\n  background: none !important;\n  color: white;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav td {\n  vertical-align: top;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav th h2{\n  font-weight: 800;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav li {\n  margin-top: 4px;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  font-size: 14pt;\n  }\n</style>",
